# endless-sky-parse

A working, tested Python conversion of the C++ parser for Endless Sky DataFiles

## How to install

```
$ pip install endless-sky-parse
```

## Development


```
$ python -m venv venv && . venv/bin/activate
$ pip install -r dev_requirements.txt
```

Run tests with

```
$ python setup.py test
```



